short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fastest to switch to tab page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When opening many tab pages in chrome, switching tab pages is very troublesome. Using tabs-switcher will make it very convenient for you to switch tab pages. Press Alt + U to open the tab list page, and then press the corresponding key to switch, it's that simple!
